The Poetic Terms:

1. Give Credit, Not Chaos.
   If you use, modify, or share this code, a little nod to Poeticlore™ would be appreciated (but not required).

2. No Paywalls, No Greed.
   You may not sell this software or any modified versions of it without prior written permission from Poeticlore™.
